<p>The <a href="http://www.doubleclick.com/privacy/faq.aspx">DoubleClick DART cookie</a> is used by Google in the ads served on the websites of its partners, such as websites displaying AdSense ads or participating in Google certified ad networks. When users visit a partner&#8217;s website and either view or click on an ad, a cookie may be dropped on that end user&#8217;s browser. The data gathered from these cookies will be used to help better serve and manage ads on the publisher&#8217;s site(s) and across the web.</p>
